{
  "stem": "1736.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's the last time I saw them, that was-- together with my brother and sister.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and she went back to Aken and then, we went on from there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I must say here, we met-- we got in touch with an organization in Berlin that was taking care of homeless people-- Jewish people, or people in need-- and I can't remember the title of it.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were put in touch with an organization that was attempting and giving guidance to young children to escape, and, of course, helping them to do so.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "An organization which was led by a lady [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with the name of Recha Freier.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "R-E-C-H-A, Recha.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Freier.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it was F-R-E-I-E-R.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was the wife of a Berlin rabbi.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I believe they were separated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she had taken it up on herself--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She would have been in her 40s.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To me, at the time, she looked like an old lady.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And of course, it's also the way she dressed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She always had long dresses on and all this sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I must add here, there was another aspect which was rather important.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Recha had taken it upon herself to, particularly, take children who were of originally Polish background.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because for some peculiar reasons, whenever there were places-- like, for instance, there were places given to young children transports to go to Switzerland or to Sweden-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the preference was always given to young German Jewish kids.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Meaning Jews coming from the east.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were, [INAUDIBLE] at the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were looked down, not unlike what happened when the [INAUDIBLE] came to this country by the establishment Jews in Australia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know the history a little bit about that.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
